txt.en:
Upon a mountain hill, the lonely peak to your back, a wyrm slithers by your side.
Upon a mountain hill, a sturdy bridge and island touched by our people, a gorged snake below.
In the perilous north, a dragon's hoard glimmers in the darkness.
The Stave of Veluk-zámok lies here within Glitgróf, in the clutches of Etterfang. To seek the Stave is to seek Thafar-gathol. Beware.
